                "track": "Strength; Frequency 1/round for 6 rounds",
                "effect": "At the dead state, the victim\u2019s body disintegrates into dust. A creature that dies as a result of greater dust manta toxin can only be brought back to life by spells such as <i>miracle</i>, <i>wish</i>, or another similarly powerful effect.",
